  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK340">
<l>pukki lamaintiṉṟu kollō vuṭampiṉuṭ</l>
<l>ṭucci lirunta vuyirkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It seems as if the soul, which takes a temporary shelter in a body, had not attained a home.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
